data.description:
HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! 
Your dream home awaits in Bozeman, MT! This captivating 4 bed, 3 bath single-family home in the Southbridge subdivision. Enjoy 2200 sq ft of living space, an open floor plan, and modern amenities like a gas fireplace. The main-level master suite and 2nd-story guest ensuite offer comfort and privacy. Plus, a fenced yard adds to the appeal. With MSU and mountain recreation nearby, it's the perfect location. Don't miss out on this gem
